\n<Sonoda Kohei>(.........How did it come to this?)

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(......L-Let's calm down here for a moment and
organize our memories.)
Let's think about how we got to this point
…此処に至った経緯を考える。

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(Well... it's just speculation. There might be
some of my desires mixed in...)

I was called out from behind, and all my thoughts
up until now were blown away. I pretended to be
calm and turned towards her while still sitting on
the bed.

\n<Sonoda Kohei>...  Note: The text in Japanese represents a pause
or hesitation.

Minato Neon, dressed in a defenseless manner with
just a bath towel wrapped around, sits down next
to me.

\n<Minato Neon>But... it really exists, huh? A bathroom that's
completely exposed like that...
\n<Sonoda Kohei>Ah... I'll just say this, but I...

\n<Minato Neon>Don't worry... I trust you. Sonoda-san wouldn't
peek or anything.

Previously Translated Text: Since I had been going
to the monitor room, I feel really guilty.
\n<Minato Neon>Or... is there no value in looking at it?
\n<Sonoda Kohei>It's not about that. It's a matter of morals.
\n<Minato Neon>Then... what if I said I don't mind being seen?

\n<Sonoda Kohei>Well... no, please stop joking. I'll also take a
quick shower.
Minato Neon stands up before I can even stand up.

\n<Minato Neon>If it's Sonoda-san... then it's fine. So, please
look at me properly...

Neon gently placed her hand on her chest, where
she had secured the bath towel, and after a
momentary hesitation, slowly untied it.

And... the only piece of fabric that was covering
her fell to the ground at her feet.

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(When I called out to Neon in front of that
convenience store, her behavior was strange...)

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(He was operating his smartphone... What was he
looking at? No... was he investigating something?)

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(Wasn't he searching for nearby hotels? If that's
the case, it all makes sense...)

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(If... it wasn't just a coincidence, then it would
mean that I was led here by Neon.)

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(The purpose... Is it that kind of thing... Should
I do it? Is Neon really...)

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(First of all... it wouldn't work if she didn't
already know this place. I find it hard to believe
that Neon, who came from the countryside, would
have such familiarity with this area...)

And there, I remembered Neon's suspicious
behavior.

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(Yes... Neon complained of not feeling well... and
she seemed unable to drive, so we decided to take
a break for now.)

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(Coincidentally, this hotel happened to be near
where we parked...)

\n<Sonoda Kohei>(No... Is it really just a coincidence? Can
something like that really happen by chance...?)
